.Dd $Mdocdate: August 17 2021 $
.Dt UHIDPP 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm uhidpp
.Nd Logitech HID++ devices
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "uhidpp* at uhidev?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for Logitech HID++ devices.
It exposes a collection of battery sensor values which are made available
through the
.Xr sysctl 8
interface.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr uhidev 4 ,
.Xr usb 4 ,
.Xr sensorsd 8 ,
.Xr sysctl 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 6.9 .
